{"tid":149340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★停不了的自殺！今次打孖上2個廢中！","createTime":"2017-03-09T08:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T09:03:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e131ce8c20efd4905a43bc2707ba73d11a95a2f","tid":149340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:28:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170309/bkn-20170309035026119-0309_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170309%2Fbkn-20170309035026119-0309_00822_001.html&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9osVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=90b6fa7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170309/bkn-20170309035026119-0309_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一對分別姓呂（59歲）及姓吳（56歲）夫婦，今晨2時許，駕乘凌志私家車沿昂船洲大橋駛往機場方向，至近橋面中段位置停車。管制區職員透過閉路電視見到兩人落車，未幾失去其蹤影，到場後只發現私家車，車內插有車匙，惟空無一人，於是報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員趕至現場，發現欄杆上有鞋印，在私家車內檢獲該對男女的身份證及一封遺書"},{"pid":"aa3ce0720a8364845096a00e534bfdbf23216388","tid":149340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:29:34.000Z","msg":"多到出唔切post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52d139b68e7f099b783656fa386e5ee8166ee1a","tid":149340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae3d3e7d069c208a736cbf02eedcf82ec8f161d","tid":149340,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"呢2日 以為係香港自殺日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hk